{
  "name": "Ram Wings (Rosemary, Ancho, Molasses Glazed Chicken Wings) – Acronymically Delicious",
  "author": "Chef John",
  "description": "Overly contrived recipes are usually a bad idea, but these rosemary, ancho, and molasses glazed chicken wings really did come out very well, despite the fact that those ingredients were only chosen because they spelled out the word, “ram.”",
  "servings": "4 large portions",
  "ingredient_sections": [
    {
